<doc id='bbc_140828_ebola_warning_5steps' type='mono' source_url='http://www.bbc.co.uk/swahili/habari/2014/08/140828_ebola_warning_5steps' term='ebola'>
Njia 5 za kuepuka virusi  hatari vya Ebola
